    bibo:journal "Zootaxa" ;
    bibo:pubDate "2017-05-05" ;
    bibo:startPage "499" ;
    bibo:volume "4317" ;
    dc:creator "Fery, Hans" ;
    dc:date "2017" ;
    dc:title "A new classification of the tribe Hygrotini Portevin, 1929 (Coleoptera: Dytiscidae: Hydroporinae)" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.884786>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.884772>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.884770> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.884786>
    dc:description "FIGURES 49 – 55. (49 – 53): Epipleuron with oblique epipleural carina and genicular fossa of: (49) Clemnius (s. str.) berneri, (50) Hygrotus (Leptolambus) polonicus polonicus, (51) H. (Coelambus) caspius, (52) H. (Leptolambus) impressopunctatus and (53) Rhithrodytes agnus; epipleural carina (c) and inner margin of epipleuron (m) including angle mentioned in diagnoses of subgenera. (54 – 55): Elytral margin in lateral view of: (54) H. (Coelambus) caspius (strongly ascending to shoulder) and (55) Clemnius (s. str.) berneri (moderately ascending to shoulder) (Figs 52 and 53 are reproduced from Fery 2013 and from Fery 2016 with the permissions of F. Gusenleitner, Linz, Austria, and G. Foster, Ayr, UK, respectively)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/884786/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.884772>
    dc:description "FIGURES 3 – 4. Antennal cavities of: (3) Hydroporus dorsalis (Hydroporini) and (4) Hygrotus (Leptolambus) lagari (Fery, 1992) (a: carina delimiting capsule for scape; b: fronto-lateral border of clypeus; c: second carina)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/884772/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.884770>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Dendrogram showing the new classification of Hygrotini. A number of species without molecular data (no voucher number) have been inserted near morphologically similar species with molecular data. Acronyms refer to biogeographical regions." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/884770/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

